<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
   <head>
      <style>
         table {
         font-family: arial, sans-serif;
         border-collapse: collapse;
         width: 100%;
         }
         td, th {
         border: 1px solid #dddddd;
         text-align: left;
         padding: 8px;
         }
         th {
         background-color: #dddddd;
         }
      </style>
   </head>
   <body>
      <p> 
         Hi Team,
      </p>
      <p>
         Automated monitoring has detected one or more errors in Apex code and/or Flow processes in the following Salesforce environment:
      </p>
      <p> 
         <b>Org Name:</b> {ORGNAME}
         <br/>
         <b>Org Id:</b> {ORGID}
         <br/>
         <b>Date:</b> {DATE}
      </p>
      {ERRORSDETAILS}
      <br/>
      <br/>
      <p> 
         Thanks
      </p>
   </body>
</html>